main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 1553/2000 is amended as follows:
1. in Article 2, paragraph 1, the terms "from 1 to 11 September 2000" are replaced by "from 18 to 22 September 2000";
2. in Article 2, paragraph 6, the terms "on 1 September 2000" are replaced by "on 18 September 2000";
3. in Article 3, the terms "within five working days" are replaced by "within four working days";
4. in Article 4, the terms "by 25 October 2000" are replaced by "31 October 2000".
